{"title":"老炉工","authors":["王荫昌"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":3,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老炉工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京市机械施工公司工人　王荫昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“铁人”装胸中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身带铁味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱厂老炉工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬是不知累。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上班坚守岗位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下班小车一推，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走遍全厂各个角落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处捡宝贝——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沾满油污的棉纱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没烧透的煤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺丝、垫圈、破手套……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点滴滴车上汇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导刻心扉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厉行节约最可贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收“徒”开篇头句话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大庆有个回收队……”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}